  <p style="margin: 0 0 16px;">아래 버튼을 눌러 로그인하세요.</p>
  <p style="margin: 0 0 20px;">
    <a href="<%= @magic_link %>" style="display: inline-block; padding: 10px 16px; background: #111827; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600;">
